---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContentHero from '../../components/ContentHero.astro';
import TakeAction from '../../components/TakeAction.astro';
---

<Layout title="Buy more land for restoration">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<ContentHero
		title="Buy more land for restoration"
		imgSrc="/hero-land-fund.jpg"
		imgAlt="Green rolling hills with patches of trees and stone fences"
	/>

	<!-- Main Content with Donorbox Widget -->
	<section class="PageSection" data-layout="sidebar-right">
		<div class="PageSection__content">
			<!-- Left: Main Content (67%) -->
			<div>
				<div class="prose">
					<p>
						Protect Earth does a lot more than just plant trees - we create lasting, thriving
						woodlands, wetlands, and ecosystems. Our Land Fund is dedicated solely to purchasing
						land for reforestation and rewilding, ensuring it is protected forever.
					</p>
					<p>
						We love collaborating with landowners - so far, we've helped over 60 farms, hotels,
						local councils, schools, parks, and even wedding venues bring more trees to their land.
						But some of our most exciting work happens when we create new diverse nature reserves
						from scratch.
					</p>
					<p>Thanks to generous donations, we've already transformed places like:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>
							<a href="/sites/high-wood-7xpjt">High Wood</a> - A flourishing new woodland where wildlife
							is returning.
						</li>
						<li>
							<a href="/sites/goytrewood">Goytre Wood</a> - A rewilded space where nature and people can
							thrive together.
						</li>
						<li>
							Bath Woodland & Wetland - A diverse landscape that's helping restore natural
							ecosystems.
						</li>
					</ul>
					<p>
						With your support, we can buy more land, create more forests, begin landscape-scale
						restoration with our new neighbours, and protect more nature - permanently.
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>
							Every pound donated to the Land Fund goes directly toward securing and restoring new
							woodlands and ecosystems.
						</strong>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Right: Donorbox Widget (33%) -->
			<div>
				<div class="sticky">
					<script src="https://donorbox.org/widget.js" paypalExpress="true"></script>
					<iframe
						src="https://donorbox.org/embed/protect-earth?language=en"
						name="donorbox"
						allowpaymentrequest="allowpaymentrequest"
						seamless="seamless"
						frameborder="0"
						scrolling="no"
						height="700px"
						class="w-full"
						style="min-width: 250px; max-height:none!important"
						allow="payment"></iframe>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<TakeAction />
</Layout>
